milestones.description: Stelling and Kervezee's 59-run partnership is NED's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 42 between Lefebvre and Henk-Jan Mol
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (14) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
Peter Borren has conceded the most runs in an innings (94) in ODIs for NED, going past Tim de Leede's record of 69
This is the highest match aggregate (691) involving teams Sri Lanka & Netherlands in ODIs
Sri Lanka's 443 is the highest total in ODIs, surpassing South Africa's 438
Jayasuriya has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (363), going past Inzamam-ul-Haq
